::
:: (C:\opt\b\lief-win\_build_env) (base) C:\opt\b\lief-win\work\build-pylief>C:\opt\b\lief-win\_h_env\python.exe -c "import lief"
:: Fatal Python error: _PyInterpreterState_Get(): no current thread state
